[ nc_sim ]
Neuronal culture simulator
==========================
A small python package to simulate the growth (axons.*) and activity (neurons.*) of neuronal cultures in environment with obstacles

by: Akke Mats Houben (akkemats.houben@ub.edu -- akkeh.github.io)

=========================
To get started, use example/example.py

=========================
Requirements:
    - numpy
    - matplotlib (optional)

=========================
When using this code, please cite:
    A.M. Houben, J. Garcia-Ojalvo & J. Soriano, Role of connectivity anisotropies in the dynamics of cultured neuronal networks, arXiv:2501.04427 (2025)
